      <xrcs:title religion="christianity">What is Marriage?</xrcs:title>
      <xrcs:title>What is Marriage in Christianity?</xrcs:title>
      <xrcs:content>
        Marriage is a union between two people before God.
        It is traditionally between a man and a woman, although many Liberal Christians accept a broader definition of marriage.
      </xrcs:content>
      <xrcs:further>
        <a href="https://www.christianforums.com/threads/what-is-marriage.60086/">What is marriage? | Christian Forums</a>
