      <xrcs:title>How Long Does Marriage Last?</xrcs:title>
      <xrcs:content>
        <p>
          It's a common misconception that marriage is forever. It's not.<xrcs:footnote name="finite-marriage" />
          There are several ways a marriage can end:
          <ul>
            <li>Divorce</li>
            <li>Annullment</li>
            <li>Death</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
      </xrcs:content>
      <xrcs:footnotes>
        <xrcs:footnote name="finite-marriage">In Mormonism, marriage <i>is</i> eternal;
          see the further reading section.</xrcs:footnote>
      </xrcs:footnotes>
